OL,3,CChildren should get chickenpox
OL,4,Cvaccine on the NHS, experts tell
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FChildren should be able to get the
OL,8,Fchickenpox vaccine on the NHS,
OL,9,Fscientists advising the government
OL,10,Fhave recommended.
OL,12,FThe jab should be given to youngsters
OL,13,Fin two doses when they are aged 12
OL,14,Fmonths and 18 months, The Joint
OL,15,FCommittee on Vaccination and
OL,16,FImmunisation (JCVI) said.
OL,18,FCurrently the vaccine is available
OL,19,Fprivately in the UK and costs around
OL,20,F#150 for the full course of two doses.
